lead_paragraph: Team Sky are co-operating fully with a UK Anti-Doping investigation into a package sent to Bradley Wiggins at the end of the 2011 Dauphine race and are "confident" no wrongdoing will be found, they said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Cycling: Team Sky Confident UKAD Will Find No Wrongdoing
